FBIS3-53133 "drnes008_a_94006" FBIS-NES-94-008 Document Type:Daily Report 12 Jan 1994 ARAB AFRICA Algeria HAMAS Urges `Responsibility' To Be Accepted LD1101215694 Algiers ENTV Television Network in Arabic 1900 GMT 11 Jan 94 LD1101215694 Algiers ENTV Television Network Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] HAMAS [Islamic Society Movement] issued a statement in which it appealed to the Algerian people and all the sides in the opposition to shoulder the historic responsibility before God and before the nation. In its appeal to the authority and the Islamic Salvation Front (FIS) and other parties and forces, Hamas underlines the need to participate in ending bloodshed, the destruction of installations, the threatening of worshipers, and for the need to stop statements for scoring one-upmanship and for bargaining. All must work for restoring tranquillity and must safeguard the supreme interest of the homeland.
